[00:12.94]Does grandmother seem pleased to get a card from Jimmy? Why/Why not?|奶奶收到吉米送的卡片时，看起来很高兴吗？为什么呢？
[00:23.61]Read Jimmy's card to me please, Penny.|请把吉米的卡片内容读给我听，佩妮。
[00:28.94]'I have just arrived in Scotland and I'm staying at a Youth Hostel.'|我刚到苏格兰，现在住在一家青年旅舍里。
[00:37.16]Eh?|嗯？
